  <li>Hansen, Tanja M. (2021) "Fifty Shades of Terrorist Credit-Taking: A Review of the Existing Scholarship on Terrorist Credit-Taking", <span class="emphasized">International Studies Review</span>, Volume 23, Issue 4, Pages 1370-1398.</li>
  <p> </p>
  <li>Hansen, Tanja M. (2021) <span class="emphasized">Terrorism - Why Not Claim It While You're at It?</span> PhD Dissertation, Political Science, University of Southern Denmark, May 2021.</li>
  
